The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 60

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

The winners of the final challenge week are announced and two teams will head into the auction with almost $30,000 off their reserves. The contestants move out of the block and welcome in the punters at the open for inspection day.
